              pharetra.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="jp_faq_item">
            <h4>02. Upload a profile picture</h4>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
              Pellentesque elementum mi at erat egestas, nec porta diam
